      "content": "i get what you're saying about the risks but my doctor is so hard to reach and it takes weeks to get an appointment... i really just want to fix this now. if i did a very slow taper where i just take like half my sertraline dose for a week and then start the st johns wort, is there a specific dosage of the herb i should look for to make sure it actually works for my anxiety? i just want to do this the right way on my own.",
